@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zuevwf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((tmp - (v2 + 0.15 + v1 + 0.48)) + (0.53 - (v1 + 0.23 * v2 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (0.09 - wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.37)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
